more\n*[[90th Illinois Volunteer Infantry Regiment|90th Illinois]]: Col Timothy O'Meara ('''k'''), Ltc Owen Stuart\n*[[12th Regiment Indiana Infantry (3 years)|12th Indiana]]: Col Reuben Williams\n*[[100th Regiment Indiana Infantry|100th Indiana]]: Ltc Albert Heath\n|-\n| 2nd Brigade<ref>[[15th Michigan Volunteer Infantry Regiment|15th Michigan]] detached at Scottsborough, Alabama</ref>\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[John M. Corse]] ('''w''')\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol Charles C. Walcutt\n|\n*[[40th Illinois Volunteer Infantry Regiment|40th Illinois]]: Maj Hiram W. Hall\n*[[103rd Illinois Volunteer Infantry Regiment|103rd Illinois]]: Col William A. Dickerman\n*[[6th Iowa Volunteer Infantry Regiment|6th Iowa]]: Ltc Alexander J. Miller\n*[[46th Ohio Infantry|46th Ohio]]: Col [[Charles C. Walcutt]], Cpt Isaac N. Alexander\n|-\n| 3rd Brigade\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol [[Joseph R. Cockerill]]\n|\n*[[48th Illinois Volunteer Infantry Regiment|48th Illinois]]: Ltc Lucien Greathouse\n*[[97th Regiment Indiana Infantry|97th Indiana]]: Col [[Robert F. Catterson]]\n*[[99th Regiment Indiana Infantry|99th Indiana]]: Col Alexander Fowler\n*[[53rd Ohio Infantry|53rd Ohio]]: Col Wells S. Jones\n*[[70th Ohio Infantry|70th Ohio]]: Maj William B. Brown\n|-\n| Artillery\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCpt Henry Richardson\n|\n*[[Battery \"F\", 1st Regiment Illinois Volunteer Light Artillery|1st Illinois Light, Battery F]]: Cpt John T. Cheney\n*1st Illinois Light, Battery I: Lt Josiah H. Burton\n*1st Missouri Light, Battery D: Lt Byron M. Callender\n|}\n\n====[[XVII Corps (Union Army)|XVII Corps]]====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! width=25% | Division\n! width=25% | Brigade\n! Regiments and others\n|-\n| rowspan=4 |\nSecond Division\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[John Eugene Smith|John E. Smith]]\n| 1st Brigade\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol Jesse I. Alexander\n|\n*[[63rd Illinois Volunteer Infantry Regiment|63rd Illinois]]: Col Joseph B. McCown\n*[[48th Regiment Indiana Infantry|48th Indiana]]: Ltc Edward J. Wood\n*[[5